data.description: Ready for immediate delivery!  This home features, LOW MAINTENANCE LIVING.  The Metro District will cut the grass in the front in the summer and shovel the snow in the winter (must be 4" or more).  Brand new community club house and fitness center - the Venture Center.  Two new outdoor swimming pools.  Community dog park.  Ranch style home with a full, unfinished basement.  Just across the street from the soon-to-be developed Spree park.  Spree park will include pickle ball, tennis courts and a community garden.  Be one of the first homeowners in this brand new enclave of low maintenance homes in the fabulous Brighton Crossings community. Special grand opening price on this home!
